<h1>Glossary</h1>

<p>The framework's working vocabulary, ingested and rendered verbatim. Every term of art on
the site is one touch from its plain cut — the one-sentence definition with no term of art
inside it. Here each term carries both: the plain cut and the full entry, with the defining
document named.</p>

<dl class="glossary">
  {%- for entry in glossary %}
  <dt id="{{ entry.anchor }}" class="cjk"><strong>{{ entry.term }}</strong></dt>
  <dd class="cjk">
    {%- if entry.plain %}<span class="plain">{{ entry.plain }}</span><br>{% endif -%}
    {{ entry.html | safe }}
  </dd>
  {%- endfor %}
</dl>
